---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Project Management Software for Framing Contractors | BuildWorkPro" description="Construction management software for framing subcontractors. Track bids, manage crew, handle pay apps. Built for wood and metal framing. $79/month flat.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">For Framing Contractors</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
          Project Management for Framing Contractors
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Manage wall layouts, floor systems, and roof framing across all your jobs from one platform. Track material deliveries, schedule crews for each building or phase, and submit pay apps tied to your percent complete. BuildWorkPro keeps your framing operation running tight.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <!-- TODO: Restore "Start free trial" button at launch -->
          <span class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-400 rounded-xl cursor-default">Coming Soon</span>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">We're preparing for launch. Internal testing in progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why framing contractors use BuildWorkPro -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">Why framing contractors use BuildWorkPro</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5M3.75 3v18m16.5-18v18M5.25 3h13.5M5.25 21h13.5M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Organize by building and phase</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Break multi-building projects into phases -- sill plates, wall framing, floor systems, roof trusses, and sheathing. Track completion by building so you always know where your crews stand.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Bid from material takeoffs</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Build estimates based on board feet, stud counts, and truss packages. Include labor for wall layout, standing walls, floor deck, and roof framing with your production rates per square foot.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0H6.375m11.25 0h3.375a1.125 1.125 0 001.125-1.125V14.25m0 0V5.625m0 8.625h-3.75m0 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5-1.5V5.625m5.25 0h-5.25m0 0H9.375m0 0H3.375m6 0V3.75m0 1.875h5.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Track material deliveries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Log lumber drops, truss deliveries, and hardware shipments. Know when materials are on site so your crew shows up ready to work, not waiting on a truck that hasn't arrived.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Pay apps by phase and building</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Generate pay applications with line items for each building and phase. Bill for first-floor walls, second-floor deck, roof framing, and sheathing separately with accurate percent complete.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Schedule crews across subdivisions</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Assign framing crews to buildings and lots. Balance your workforce between multi-family and single-family projects, move crews as buildings dry in, and keep production on pace.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2.5 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Inspection-ready documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Log framing inspections, nailing patterns, hold-down placements, and shear wall details. Keep daily reports that document what was built and what was inspected on every unit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What's included -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-8">Everything you need at one flat price</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-slate-500 mb-8">$79/month for unlimited users and projects. No per-user fees.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Unlimited users</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Unlimited projects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Bids & estimates</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Pay applications</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Change orders</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Site logs & daily reports</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Gantt charts & scheduling</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Sales pipeline & CRM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Time tracking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Role-based permissions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Reports & analytics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Document management</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Ready to streamline your framing business?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-8">Join other framing contractors who've ditched spreadsheets for BuildWorkPro.</p>
      <!-- TODO: Restore "Start free trial" button at launch -->
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-400 rounded-xl cursor-default">Coming Soon</span>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
